  "closed_at": "2017-01-11T03:02:17Z",
  "body": "代码如下：\r\n```\r\n<template>\r\n  <div class=\"list-wrap\">\r\n    <list class=\"menu\">\r\n      <cell class=\"menu-item\" repeat=\"menu\">\r\n        <text class=\"menu-name\">{{ name }}</text>\r\n      </cell>\r\n    </list>\r\n  </div>\r\n</template>\r\n<script>\r\n  module.exports = {\r\n    data: {\r\n      menu: [\r\n        { name: 1 },\r\n        { name: 2 },\r\n        { name: 3 },\r\n        { name: 4 },\r\n        { name: 5 },\r\n        { name: 6 },\r\n        { name: 7 },\r\n        { name: 8 },\r\n        { name: 9 },\r\n        { name: 10 },\r\n        { name: 11 },\r\n        { name: 12 },\r\n        { name: 13 },\r\n        { name: 14 },\r\n        { name: 15 },\r\n        { name: 16 },\r\n        { name: 17 },\r\n      ],\r\n    },\r\n  };\r\n</script>\r\n<style>\r\n  .list-wrap {\r\n    flex-direction: row;\r\n    flex: 1;\r\n    background-color: #fff;\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  .menu {\r\n    width: 100px;\r\n    background-color: blue;\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  .menu-name {\r\n    padding-left: 20px;\r\n    padding-right: 20px;\r\n    padding-top: 36px;\r\n    padding-bottom: 36px;\r\n    lines: 3;\r\n    text-overflow: ellipsis;\r\n    color: #666;\r\n    font-size: 24px;\r\n  }\r\n  \r\n  .menu-item {\r\n    border-top-width: 1px;\r\n    border-top-style: solid;\r\n    border-top-color: #ededed;\r\n  }\r\n</style>\r\n\r\n```\r\n\r\n期望\b list 的宽度为100px，但实际是全屏的。\r\n\r\n设备版本和效果截图如下：\r\n![wechatimg18](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/7367678/21797629/262e1356-d74b-11e6-882c-11506c3b9bf9.jpeg)\r\n![wechatimg20](https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/7367678/21797645/452d0ae6-d74b-11e6-825e-aa7b9769f667.jpeg)\r\n\r\n"
